addSource

public JUnitCommand addSource(java.lang.String source)
                       throws TablesawException
Path to source file to include. Because it may be easier to get the source path instead of the full class name this method allows you to enter the path to the java file. The file is then parsed for the package declaration in order to build the full class name.

Parameters:
source - path to java source file.
